{"tid":849326,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黑人家庭到西湖玩 慘被強國人當「道具」合照","createTime":"2018-10-05T15:09:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-05T15:49:52.000Z","uid":28765,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2c577e24ffd54811e97fdfffaf77f8882f4817ca","tid":849326,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T15:09:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_php1dIA31.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_php1dIA31.png&h=b194058e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一個非裔家庭原本坐在路邊休息，卻有中國客跑來要合照，讓他們相當尷尬。（圖擷自微博）<br />\n<br />\n2018-10-05 22:21<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕最近是中國的十一長假，不少中國人都出去玩。不過一個到中國遊玩的非裔家庭卻因為中國人太多遇到麻煩，他們一家人原本坐在路邊休息，卻有一堆中國客跑來要合照，讓他們相當尷尬。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpu62Kky.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpu62Kky.png&h=e5334568&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n女子抱起黑人寶寶合照。（圖擷自微博）<br />\n<br />\n綜合報導指出，最近一個黑人家庭跑到中國西湖遊玩，家長抱著小孩坐在路邊的椅子上休息，結果一群中國人卻圍了上來，還有人把他們一家當成合照「道具」。黑人家庭雖然對此感到尷尬、露出苦笑，仍然配合中國人合照，結果合照的民眾一個接著一個，更有女子在合照時將黑人小孩抱起拍照。<br />\n<br />\n這段影片在網路上引來討論，有人直言，「沒禮貌。」、「沒見過外國人？」、「太丟人了！」、「不太好吧，好像沒見過（黑人）一樣。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2572311\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2572311&d=3e2bPj8DlYzVAIsfueNW0ZUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=bee4a8bc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2572311&h=5e0b5365\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2572311</a><br />\n<br />\n笑死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8014333f03f83ea69e94909f9895046a7a5c94fc","tid":849326,"uid":198223,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T15:11:27.000Z","msg":"狗是改不了食屎的"},{"pid":